    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crystant</strong> 是一款末日生存游戏，你将扮演位于实验室中的一名受试者，在这座地下设施中，一 步步开启前方的道路，面对各种谜样的怪物与未知事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/b57c3f078f0a4899094ff3382da57210.webp?t=1771053769\" width=1500 height=45 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>引言</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从天摇地动中醒来，想起了自己当前的处境——被关在实验室里不见天日。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突然门开启了，刺眼的白光洒了进来，映入眼帘的是一条通往未知的长廊，不远处的灯光闪烁着。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你犹豫了许久，决定鼓起勇气一探究竟......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/b57c3f078f0a4899094ff3382da57210.webp?t=1771053769\" width=1500 height=45 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满未知的事件遭遇</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/b842161c02d27ac903a2fb3a62579ce9.poster.avif?t=1771053769\" width=864 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/b842161c02d27ac903a2fb3a62579ce9.webm?t=1771053769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/b842161c02d27ac903a2fb3a62579ce9.mp4?t=1771053769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备专属武器强化职业能力</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同职业装备对应专属武器，让你的角色发挥真正的实力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/426f1c85379a374cee5d18ba49f9876e.avif?t=1771053769\" width=1560 height=483 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>找寻有用资源努力生存下去</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >资源稀缺且充满风险，每一次探索都可能带来转机或危机。你需要在有限的物资中做出关键抉择，以确保自己能活着到达下一层。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 独特的类战棋回合制战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗采用可预测但充满策略深度的行动格规则，玩家必须思考移动位置、技能时机与敌人的行动模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敌人属性随机增强</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场冒险中，敌人都可能带有随机的增幅特性，使原本熟悉的怪物变得不可预测，增加挑战性并迫使玩家调整策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/365954dd30aadcb720379953c325f5e8.avif?t=1771053769\" width=1560 height=483 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更强大的敌人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在更深的区域中，你将遭遇更强大的敌人——它们拥有更高的防御力、更致命的攻击方式，以及特殊能力。小心应对，善用资源与策略才能存活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/1ce03abd4c99ebd61203643550ad2dd2.avif?t=1771053769\" width=1560 height=483 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造你的专属战斗流派</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握四大核心属性，强化队伍能力，构筑最适合你的战斗策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集特殊晶片加速提升</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习晶片可用于强化角色的核心属性，加速角色成长。<strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/2c4989f7a870fc2302517b3917cb4d62.avif?t=1771053769\" width=1560 height=483 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特定区域可使用恢复、训练、洞察功能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在休息区域中，你可以通过 <strong>恢复</strong> 进行短暂休息以回复血量；使用 <strong>训练</strong> 功能消耗晶片来强化能力，并提升获取经验值的效率；启动 <strong>洞察</strong> 则能借助监视系统远程开启地图，掌握前方区域的动向。这些功能能让你在冒险节奏间取得喘息并重新制定策略，迎接下一段更危险的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/4e623abc917a73c26de4c46758f559ac.avif?t=1771053769\" width=1560 height=879 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>场外升级解锁职业、提升能力</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在游戏中获得特殊点数，可以解锁额外的角色职业与被动强化，激励玩家不断尝试各种玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将 EXP 与 CV 带入新一轮游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次轮回后，累积的经验与特殊货币会保留下来，使下一次冒险更具优势，打造 Roguelite 式的长线成长感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集故事碎片了解灾难真相</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设施中散落着研究报告与破碎的档案，拼凑它们便能逐步揭开实验室的秘密与灾难真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/c3a48d7bf64f03081e825ebabd935371.poster.avif?t=1771053769\" width=864 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/c3a48d7bf64f03081e825ebabd935371.webm?t=1771053769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006090/extras/c3a48d7bf64f03081e825ebabd935371.mp4?t=1771053769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
